Package com.db4o.reflect

Interface Reflector

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DeepClone
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GenericReflector, JdkReflector
    public interface Reflector
extends DeepClone
    root of the reflection implementation API.

    The open reflection interface is supplied to allow to implement reflection functionality on JDKs that do not come with the java.lang.reflect.* package.

    Use configuration.commmon().reflectWith(IReflect reflector) to register the use of your implementation before opening database files.
